data.description: Why wait to build when this gorgeous move-in ready home is available now? Like new, this 2021 built Lennar's The Hartford model boasts an open and spacious floor plan. The heart of the home has a lovely center island and overlooks the dining and family room, which is great for entertaining. The dining room flows into a kitchen with plenty of counter space and stainless-steel appliances. The split plan provides the welcoming master bedroom with plenty of privacy from the other 3 bedrooms. The Master Suite includes a full bath and a walk-in closet. This home also has the benefit of leased Solar Panels.  Relax and enjoy the beautiful lake view.  The backyard has plenty of room for a pool or paver patio, and you'll get the peace of mind of a newer home with energy-efficient features all in the growing area of Saint Cloud. The Old Hickory community amenities include resort-style swimming pool with cabana, playground, and dog park.   You can't beat this location, great schools, and is close to shopping and restaurants. There are outstanding fishing areas, wildlife reserves, and hiking trails for you and your family to enjoy. Come take a look at your future home and don’t let this GEM slip away!  There is easy access to Florida Turnpike.
